properties.Name: Visit
properties.Description: A visit between two parties. The visiting party may be a party, employee or customer. The visited party may be a party, channel or store.

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Visit.

Columns.Description: The end timestamp for which the visit is in-effect.

Columns.Name: VisitNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the visit.

Columns.Name: VisitingPartyId

Columns.Name: ChannelId

Columns.Name: StoreId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Store.

Columns.Name: VisitedPartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.
